@node main "Introduction to doublylinked"

The doublylinked object provides a doubly linked list object. Each item
of such a list has a link to its successor and predecessor. The object
can be seen as an example for exec's list.

This object was designed by Barry Wills and ported to the ooep by Gregor
Goldbach.

There is an @{" example " link EMODULES:oomodules/list/doublylinked/test.e/main} available.

There is an @{" autodoc " link EMODULES:oomodules/oodoc/guides/doublylinked/main} file available or this object.

@endnode
